OL,3,C"The state stole years of my life"
OL,5,FA man who served 17 years in prison
OL,6,Fafter being wrongly convicted of rape
OL,7,Fhas hit out at an "insulting" increase
OL,8,Fin compensation for victims of
OL,9,Fmiscarriages of justice.
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Justice has announced
OL,12,Fthat the compensation cap will rise by
OL,13,F30% for those who were convicted of a
OL,14,Fcrime they did not commit.
OL,16,FThose wrongfully imprisoned for more
OL,17,Fthan 10 years will receive #1.3
OL,18,Fmillion instead of #1 million, while
OL,19,Fthose with sentences of less than 10
OL,20,Fyears will receive #650,000 rather
OL,21,Fthan #500,000.
