OL,3,C"The state stole years of my life"
OL,5,FIt is the first increase to the
OL,6,Fpayment since the scheme's
OL,7,Fintroduction in 2008.
OL,9,FBut Andrew Malkinson, who has been
OL,10,Fcampaigning with the law charity
OL,11,FAppeal to get the compensation scheme
OL,12,Foverhauled, described the change as
OL,13,F"insulting".
OL,15,FHe was wrongly convicted and jailed in
OL,16,F2004 for the rape of a 33-year-old
OL,17,Fwoman in Salford, Greater Manchester,
OL,18,Fspending 17 years in prison.
OL,26,@kD@AOUuD@AOUuD@KO]
