OL,3,C"The state stole years of my life"
OL,5,FMr Malkinson ` who was released in
OL,6,F2020 after DNA evidence proved he was
OL,7,Fnot the attacker ` said: "This change
OL,8,Fis an improvement but a below-
OL,9,Finflation increase is insulting.
OL,11,F"The state stole years of my life and
OL,12,Frobbed me of my physical and mental
OL,13,Fhealth, yet it still wants to
OL,14,Farbitrarily limit the compensation I
OL,15,Freceive to try to put myself back
OL,16,Ftogether.
OL,26,@kD@AOUoD@ZOUsD@AOU
