OL,3,C"The state stole years of my life"
OL,5,F"I'll keep fighting to abolish this
OL,6,Fcruel and arbitrary cap, along with
OL,7,Fthe brutal rules currently denying
OL,8,Fcompensation to the vast majority of
OL,9,Fwrongfully convicted people."
OL,11,FThe compensation scheme is intended to
OL,12,Fhelp individuals restart and rebuild
OL,13,Ftheir lives.
OL,15,FIt is one route through which an
OL,16,Findividual can receive compensation
OL,17,Ffor a wrongful conviction, with other
OL,18,Foptions including suing public bodies.
