OL,5,FThose claiming after miscarriages of
OL,6,Fjustice within the armed forces will
OL,7,Falso see the same rise in the cap.
OL,9,FToby Wilton, solicitor at Hickman &
OL,10,FRose who represent Mr Malkinson in his
OL,11,Fclaims for compensation, said: "While
OL,12,Fthis proposal is welcome, it does not
OL,13,Fgo nearly far enough. The current
OL,14,Fmaximum cap on compensation of #1
OL,15,Fmillion was introduced in 2008.
OL,17,F"Before that, compensation was not
OL,18,Fcapped at all and applicants received
OL,19,Fcompensation broadly in line with what
OL,20,Fthey would receive in a court of law.
OL,26,@kD@AOUsD@`OUyD@AOU
