OL,3,C"The state stole years of my life"
OL,5,F"The government should return to this
OL,6,Fsystem, removing the arbitrary cap
OL,7,Fwhich unfairly penalises those who,
OL,8,Flike Andrew Malkinson, have suffered
OL,9,Fthe longest lasting and most serious
OL,10,Fmiscarriages of justice.
OL,12,F"A 30% increase in the cap, whilst
OL,13,Fwelcome, does not come close to
OL,14,Faddressing this unfairness.
OL,26,@kD@AOUmD@AOUtD@AOU
