OL,3,C"The state stole years of my life"
OL,5,F"Increased by RPI inflation, the
OL,6,Fmeasure the courts use to uprate
OL,7,Fcompensation amounts, #1 million in
OL,8,F2008 would be closer to #2 million
OL,9,Ftoday. Increased by CPI, it would be
OL,10,F#1.65 million, more than double this
OL,11,Fproposed increase.
OL,13,F"The Government and Parliament should
OL,14,Fthink again."
OL,16,FLord Chancellor Shabana Mahmood
OL,17,Fbelieves the additional support will
OL,18,Fhelp victims of miscarriages of
OL,19,Fjustice.
