OL,5,FShe said: "Fairness is the ideal that
OL,6,Funderpins our justice system. Where it
OL,7,Fhas failed to meet that ideal, victims
OL,8,Fof devastating miscarriages of justice
OL,9,Fmust be able to rebuild their lives.
OL,11,F"This uplift will ensure victims are
OL,12,Fcompensated for the crimes they did
OL,13,Fnot commit and the years they cannot
OL,14,Fget back."
